Privacy Policy for Pakka Pets
Effective Date:
January 24th, 2024
This Privacy Policy outlines the types of personal information collected by Pakka Pets, how it is used, and the measures taken to protect your privacy. By using our mobile game, you consent to the terms outlined in this policy.
1. Information We Collect:
1.1 Personal Information:
We may collect personal information such as your name, email address, and device information when you register or use our services.
1.2 Non-Personal Information:
We may collect non-personal information, including but not limited to device type, operating system, and gameplay data, to improve our services.
2. How We Use Your Information:
2.1 Service Improvement:
We use collected information to enhance and personalize your gaming experience.
2.2 Communication:
We may use your email address to send updates, newsletters, and promotional content. You can opt-out at any time.
2.3 Analytics:
We analyze user data to improve our game features, identify trends, and optimize performance.
3. Information Sharing:
3.1 Third Parties:
We do not sell or share personal information with third parties without your consent, except as required by law.
3.2 Service Providers:
We may engage third-party service providers to assist in delivering our services. They are obligated to maintain the confidentiality of your information.
4. Security:
4.1 Data Security:
We implement industry-standard security measures to protect your personal information from unauthorized access, disclosure, or alteration.
5. Changes to Privacy Policy:
5.1 Updates:
We reserve the right to update this Privacy Policy. Users will be notified of any significant changes.
7. Contact Us:
7.1 Questions:
